I am trying to use Stagehand with an existing browser instance by connecting via CDP. However, when I manually connect to the browser using Playwright's `chromium.connectOverCDP`, retrieve the page, and pass it to `stagehand.observe({ page: pwPage })`, it throws a `StagehandInitError: Failed to resolve V3 Page from Playwright page`.

